sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator
    participant PlannerAgent
    participant CoderAgent
    participant ReviewerAgent
    participant LLM
    participant Workspace

    Orchestrator->>PlannerAgent: Start workflow
    PlannerAgent->>CoderAgent: TASK message (file + instruction)

    CoderAgent->>LLM: Generate code (Codex)
    LLM-->>CoderAgent: Generated code
    CoderAgent->>CoderAgent: Clean markdown formatting
    CoderAgent->>ReviewerAgent: REQUEST message (file + code)

    ReviewerAgent->>ReviewerAgent: Syntax check
    ReviewerAgent->>ReviewerAgent: Quality scoring
    ReviewerAgent->>ReviewerAgent: Constraint validation

    alt Quality >= 8.0
        ReviewerAgent->>Workspace: Write code to file
        ReviewerAgent->>PlannerAgent: DONE message
    else Quality < 8.0
        ReviewerAgent->>PlannerAgent: REJECT message (feedback)
        PlannerAgent->>CoderAgent: TASK message (fix instruction)
    end